**Overview**

This dashboard is a health overview related to the Anomali integration.

The dashboard is made to provide general statistics and show the health of the ingestion of indicators from Anomali.  

It shows how many parts has been enabled (Limo and ThreatStream), the ingestion rates and provides a few filters for drilling down to specific indicator types retrieved from Anomali.
